Put your golf skills to the test as you swing your way across challenging courses. For Golden Tee Arcade Classics, Incredible Technologies and Digital Eclipse have chosen six early games that allow players to experience the evolution of the world’s most popular and well-known golf arcade game. For players who want to show off their arcade and pub-gaming skills, the team also included Shuffleshot and World Class Bowling.

description:
Sabrina’s leaving the door open for the next Fortnite Festival Icon… Bruno Mars! This GRAMMY-winning megastar is expanding his record-breaking world tour with a stop in Fortnite. The World Tour Bundle is available in the Shop now, featuring:

Bruno-San Outfit: Take it 'round the world.
Bruno's Collection Back Bling: A perfect mix of retro and new.
Floating Notes Contrail: Drift on beats from Mars.
Bonde do Brunão Emote: Things are looking up!
Bonde do Brunão Jam Track: A souvenir from Brazil.
Key Charm Keytar: A real collector’s item.
Worldwide Bass: Make ‘em hear you everywhere.

And this is not a dream — the Season 9 Music Pass features the Die With A Smile Bruno Outfit based on the music video for “Die With A Smile”!

Play now: https://www.xbox.com/games/store/fortnite-festival/9MZL842T57QN

description:
Today marks the Maximum Football's full 1.0 launch, bringing with it a wave of new content, polish, and performance upgrades.

Since its initial Game Preview release, Maximum Football has grown with direct input from its passionate community. Version 1.0 delivers fresh new features and a variety of quality-of-life improvements. The game continues to evolve as a free-to-play experience that puts creative control and customization directly into players’ hands.

Play Maximum Football for free on Xbox Series X|S.

Lead your team to victory in Maximum Football, the fully customizable, free-to-play football simulation game. Build and design your team your way, recruit your roster, and call the plays to dominate the gridiron with precise, realistic gameplay in the ultimate football universe.
